rows.label: tev020402_MSG0001
rows.name:
I heard gunshots and some sort of dying wail from the
other side of the west gate.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020402_MSG0002
rows.name:
I guess one of the teams must have been fighting
with an indigen?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020402_MSG0003
rows.name:
I really hope they finally took out the aggressive
indigens that have been causing problems just outside
the city.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev020402_MSG0004
rows.name:
Because in that case, we should be able to reopen the
west gate soon![ST:wait ]
